premise_source_doc_sentence: G-Dragon was awarded Artist of the Year at the 15th Mnet Asian Music Awards following the success of his second studio album Coup d'Etat  (  2013  )  , in addition to the awards of World 's Best Entertainer and World 's Best Album at the 2014 World Music Awards .
G-Dragon debuted as a solo artist with the release of Heartbreaker in 2009 .
In 2013 , he embarked on his first worldwide tour as a solo artist , which included a four-dome tour in Japan , making him the first Korean soloist to do a dome tour .
